text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria siphonophora is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Jamaica.
text.Sources: Kelly, D.L. (1998). "Psychotria siphonophora". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33865A9815745. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33865A9815745.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
